Bugs:
Don't say if a user exists!
Don't hide buttons when on their pages (signup/settings) - just disable them!
Don't allow blank password at signup

Public API brainstorm:

A distraction is something that broke your focus. It contains the following fields:
  name: What broke your streak? Chrome, Firefox, Meeting, etc
  info: How did the distraction break your streak? URL, etc
  duration: Length in minutes that you were focusing before it was broken
  timestamp: When did the distraction occur?


POST /api/streaks/new
Params:
  distraction
  timestamp
Returns:
  URL to that streak

GET /api/streaks/(best|last)
Returns:
  distraction
